In large microwave safe bowl, melt margarine and marshmallows on HIGH for about 2 minutes, stirring after 1 minute. Stir mixture until smooth. Stir in vanilla. Add KELLOGG'S* RICE KRISPIES* cereal, stirring until well coated. Spread cereal mixture into a buttered 3.5 L (13 x 9-inch) pan. Allow to cool. Shape half cup of mixture into ball, inserting a wooden stick. Roll in coconut or chopped peanuts, if desired. Create face features with miniature marshmallows, candies or frosting. Best if served same day.